Title: Add option to set show mode in global settings
Class: feature
Compatible: incomp
Component: multisite
Date: 1612537069
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

You can now set the option for "Show more / Show less" in the global settings.
These setting applies to all user until they choose to use an own setting in
there profile.

Due to a change in the valuespec, please check your profile setting regarding
this after upgrading from an earlier 2.0 version. Upgrades from version 1.6 are
not affected.
